---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — William Verbist" description="Product and experience design leader with over twenty years delivering digital products.">

  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="about-title animate">About me.</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-body">
    <div class="container">
      <hr />

      <div class="about-grid">

        <div class="about-text animate">
          <p>
            For twenty plus years, I have been able to use my love of technology and passion for design to investigate, innovate and deliver digital experiences. And while technology inspires me with its infinite possibilities, it is people that continue to drive me forward — with the chance to bring them closer, save them time, or maybe even enrich their lives.
          </p>
          <p>
            Whether leading multidisciplinary design teams or as an individual contributor, I'm a maker at heart and love to collaborate with talented technologists and watch ideas grow.
          </p>
          <p>
            I currently lead all product design at <a href="https://www.dedrone.com" class="text-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dedrone</a>, where I was solely responsible for defining and creating C2, the company's flagship product experience, and RAVEN, a defense-grade product successfully validated with the United States Army.
          </p>
          <p>
            Previously at Amazon, I led design on nascent technology including Just Walk Out (Amazon Go) and Astro, Amazon's consumer robot. I served as a Customer Experience Bar Raiser and design bar raiser across multiple lines of business.
          </p>
        </div>

        <aside class="about-sidebar animate">

          <div class="sidebar-block">
            <h3 class="sidebar-label eyebrow">Areas of expertise</h3>
            <ul class="sidebar-list">
              <li>Experience and product design</li>
              <li>Product management, strategy and vision</li>
              <li>Usability research, testing and analysis</li>
              <li>Design management and creative direction</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-block">
            <h3 class="sidebar-label eyebrow">Experience</h3>
            <ul class="exp-list">
              {[
                { company: 'Dedrone', role: 'Principal Product Designer', period: '2023 — Present' },
                { company: 'Axon', role: 'Principal UX Designer', period: '2022 — 2023' },
                { company: 'Amazon', role: 'Principal UX Designer', period: '2019 — 2022' },
              ].map(job => (
                <li class="exp-item">
                  <div class="exp-company">{job.company}</div>
                  <div class="exp-role">{job.role}</div>
                  <div class="exp-period">{job.period}</div>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-block">
            <h3 class="sidebar-label eyebrow">Contact</h3>
            <a href="mailto:hello@getvist.com" class="contact-email text-link">hello@getvist.com</a>
          </div>

        </aside>

      </div>

      <hr />
      <p class="closing-note animate">
        Much of my work is confidential and cannot be shared, but <a href="mailto:hello@getvist.com" class="text-link">drop me a line</a> and we can talk.
      </p>

    </div>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding: 6rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  }

  .about-body {
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 1.3rem;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  /* SIDEBAR */
  .sidebar-block {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .sidebar-label {
    font-family: var(--sans);
  }

  .sidebar-list {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .sidebar-list li {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .sidebar-list li:first-child {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* EXP LIST */
  .exp-list {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .exp-item {
    padding: 0.8rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .exp-item:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }

  .exp-company {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .exp-role {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.1rem;
  }

  .exp-period {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .contact-email {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .closing-note {
    font-style: italic;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .about-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }
  }
</style>
